Advanced Micro Devices to Invest 500 Million Ringgit in Malaysia

-- B y   M a n i r a j a n   R a m a s a m y
-- 
2011-06-13T07:30:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/advanced-micro-devices-to-invest-500-million-ringgit-in-malaysia.html
Advanced Micro Devices Inc. (AMD)  will
invest 500 million ringgit ($164 million) in expanding its
Malaysian global services center by December 2013, Prime
Minister Najib Razak said in a statement in  Kuala Lumpur  today.  The company has a services center in Cyberjaya, outside of
the capital.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story:
Manirajan Ramasamy in Kuala Lumpur at 
 rmanirajan@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Barry Porter in Kuala Lumpur at 
 bporter10@bloomberg.net . 